      <title>新加坡交易员对 11 亿美元欺诈行为不认罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/singapore-businessman-faces-trial-over-1-1-billion-nickel-scam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名前会计师被指控实施了震惊新加坡商界的数十亿美元的镍币诈骗案，周二他对包括欺诈和洗钱在内的 42 项指控表示不认罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/singapore-businessman-faces-trial-over-1-1-billion-nickel-scam</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 05:01:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价反弹，交易员权衡特朗普关税和停火希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价从前一天的下跌中反弹，同时交易员评估了当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的新关税威胁以及以色列和真主党在停火协议上取得的进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 23:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：特朗普关税威胁引发救济性反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁征收额外关税，并加剧了人们对其“美国优先”政策的担忧，交易员们抑制了本周初推动美国国债和全球股市上涨的缓解性反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:35:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
